king for the sum of the values of $3j$ from $j = 1$ to $j = 3$. \n", "###Evaluating\n\n$\\begin{align} \\large\\displaystyle\\sum\\limits_{j=1}^{3 }{({3j})}&= (3(\\blueD1)) + (3(\\blueD2)) + (3(\\blueD3)) \\\\\\\\\n&= 3 + 6 + 9 \\\\\\\\\n&= 18\\end{align}$", "###The answer\n\n$\\large\\displaystyle\\sum\\limits_{j=1}^{3 }{({3j})}=18$"], "widget_types": ["numeric-input"], "answer_data": {"numeric-input 1": {"type": "numeric-input", "answers": [{"maxError": null, "message": "", "simplify": "required", "status": "correct", "strict": false, "value": 18}]}}}, {"item_id": "80f751e9706e557b9e23b749768245bc", "question_content": "$\\large\\displaystyle\\sum\\limits_{k=0}^{2 }{{(2k+2)}}=$ [[☃ numeric-input 1]]\n", "hints": ["###What is the question asking for?\n\n$\\sum$ tells us to find the sum.\n\nThe question is asking for the sum of the values of $2k+2$ from $k = 0$ to $k = 2$. ", "###Evaluating\n\n$\\begin{align} \\large\\displaystyle\\sum\\limits_{k=0}^{2 }{({2k+2})}&= (2(\\blueD 0)+2) + (2(\\blueD 1)+2) + (2(\\blueD 2)+2) \\\\\\\\\n&= 2 + 4 + 6 \\\\\\\\\n&= 12\\end{align}$", "###The answer\n\n$\\large\\displaystyle\\sum\\limits_{k=0}^{2 }{({2k+2})}=12$"], "widget_types": ["numeric-input"], "answer_data": {"numeric-input 1": {"type": "numeric-input", "answers": [{"maxError": null, "message": "", "simplify": "required", "status": "correct", "strict": false, "value": 12}]}}}, {"item_id": "898499b774a25974aac8e34ddd58b098", "question_content": "$\\large\\displaystyle\\sum\\limits_{k=1}^{3 }{{(k-4)}}=$ [[☃ numeric-input 1]]\n", "hints": ["###What is the question asking for?\n\n$\\sum$ tells us to find the sum.\n\nThe question is asking for the sum of the values of $k-4$ from $k = 1$ to $k = 3$. \n", "###Evaluating\n\n$\\begin{align} \\large\\displaystyle\\sum\\limits_{k=1}^{3 }{({k-4})}&= (\\blueD1-4) + (\\blueD2-4) + (\\blueD3-4) \\\\\\\\\n&= -3 + (-2) + (-1) \\\\\\\\\n&= -6\\end{align}$", "###The answer\n\n$\\large\\displaystyle\\sum\\limits_{k=1}^{3 }{({k-4})}=-6$"], "w