 1]]\n", "hints": ["###What is the question asking for?\n\n$\\sum$ tells us to find the sum.\n\nThe question is asking for the sum of the values of $-n$ from $n = 0$ to $n = 2$. \n", "###Evaluating\n\n$\\begin{align} \\large\\displaystyle\\sum\\limits_{n=0}^{2 }{({-n})}&= (-\\blueD0) + (-\\blueD1) + (-\\blueD2) \\\\\\\\\n&= 0 + (-1) + (-2) \\\\\\\\\n&= -3\\end{align}$", "###The answer\n\n$\\large\\displaystyle\\sum\\limits_{n=0}^{2 }{({-n})}=-3$"], "widget_types": ["numeric-input"], "answer_data": {"numeric-input 1": {"type": "numeric-input", "answers": [{"maxError": null, "message": "", "simplify": "required", "status": "correct", "strict": false, "value": -3}]}}}, {"item_id": "2bc103300363548694246b0e3b4cbc06", "question_content": "$\\large\\displaystyle\\sum\\limits_{n=0}^{1 }{{(n+6)}}=$ [[☃ numeric-input 1]]\n", "hints": ["###What is the question asking for?\n\n$\\sum$ tells us to find the sum.\n\nThe question is asking for the sum of the values of $n+6$ from $n = 0$ to $n = 1$. \n", "###Evaluating\n\n$\\begin{align} \\large\\displaystyle\\sum\\limits_{n=0}^{1 }{({n+6})}&= (\\blueD0+6) + (\\blueD1+6) \\\\\\\\\n&= 6 + 7 \\\\\\\\\n&= 13\\end{align}$", "###The answer\n\n$\\large\\displaystyle\\sum\\limits_{n=0}^{1 }{({n+6})}=13$"], "widget_types": ["numeric-input"], "answer_data": {"numeric-input 1": {"type": "numeric-input", "answers": [{"maxError": null, "message": "", "simplify": "required", "status": "correct", "strict": false, "value": 13}]}}}, {"item_id": "54d00fca0a69571bafafad6a3874e442", "question_content": "$\\large\\displaystyle\\sum\\limits_{j=1}^{2 }{{(5j)}}=$ [[☃ numeric-input 1]]\n", "hints": ["###What is the question asking for?\n\n$\\sum$ tells us to find the sum.\n\nThe question is asking for the sum of the values of $5j$ from $j = 1$ to $j = 2$. \n", "###Evaluating\n\n$\\begin{align} \\large\\displaystyle\\sum\\limits_{j=1}^{2 }{({5j})}&= (5(\\blueD1)) + (5(\\blueD2)) \\\\\\\\\n&= 5 + 10 \\\\\\\\\n&= 15\\end{align}$", "###The answer\n\n$\\large\\