er\n\n$\\large\\displaystyle\\sum\\limits_{t=0}^{1 }{({4-t})}=7$"], "widget_types": ["numeric-input"], "answer_data": {"numeric-input 1": {"type": "numeric-input", "answers": [{"maxError": null, "message": "", "simplify": "required", "status": "correct", "strict": false, "value": 7}]}}}, {"item_id": "be706c44940351bf8a9dc76161aefb96", "question_content": "$\\large\\displaystyle\\sum\\limits_{j=1}^{2 }{{(j^2 + 1)}}=$ [[☃ numeric-input 1]]\n", "hints": ["###What is the question asking for?\n\n$\\sum$ tells us to find the sum.\n\nThe question is asking for the sum of the values of $j^2 + 1$ from $j = 1$ to $j = 2$. \n", "###Evaluating\n\n$\\begin{align} \\large\\displaystyle\\sum\\limits_{j=1}^{2 }{({j^2 + 1})}&= (\\blueD1^2 + 1) + (\\blueD2^2 + 1) \\\\\\\\\n&= 2 + 5 \\\\\\\\\n&= 7\\end{align}$", "###The answer\n\n$\\large\\displaystyle\\sum\\limits_{j=1}^{2 }{({j^2 + 1})}=7$"], "widget_types": ["numeric-input"], "answer_data": {"numeric-input 1": {"type": "numeric-input", "answers": [{"maxError": null, "message": "", "simplify": "required", "status": "correct", "strict": false, "value": 7}]}}}, {"item_id": "c511a297427f56138bd8e0c09b8be58e", "question_content": "$\\large\\displaystyle\\sum\\limits_{k=0}^{1 }{{(2-k)}}=$ [[☃ numeric-input 1]]\n", "hints": ["###What is the question asking for?\n\n$\\sum$ tells us to find the sum.\n\nThe question is asking for the sum of the values of $2-k$ from $k = 0$ to $k = 1$. \n", "###Evaluating\n\n$\\begin{align} \\large\\displaystyle\\sum\\limits_{k=0}^{1 }{({2-k})}&= (2-\\blueD0) + (2-\\blueD1) \\\\\\\\\n&= 2 + 1 \\\\\\\\\n&= 3\\end{align}$", "###The answer\n\n$\\large\\displaystyle\\sum\\limits_{k=0}^{1 }{({2-k})}=3$"], "widget_types": ["numeric-input"], "answer_data": {"numeric-input 1": {"type": "numeric-input", "answers": [{"maxError": null, "message": "", "simplify": "required", "status": "correct", "strict": false, "value": 3}]}}}, {"item_id": "dce3b34f8634516dab0c0b21512a3424", "question_content": "$\\large\\displaystyle\\